Notes on a Scandal is a 2006 British psychological thriller-drama film , adapted from the 2003 novel of the same name by ZoÃ« Heller .
The screenplay was written by Patrick Marber and the film was directed by Richard Eyre and starred Judi Dench and Cate Blanchett .
The soundtrack was composed by Philip Glass .
It was nominated for four Academy Awards -- Best Actress , Best Supporting Actress , Best Adapted Screenplay , and Best Original Score .